Project : invcat2d
Author  : baruken (baruken@oconsultorfinanceiro.com)
Created : 10/01/2011

Description:

This project is a work-in-progress 2d game using SDL. The objective is to create a sidescrolling space shooter.

Note:
In order to test the sprite engine I've used megaman sprite, but this will be replaced by a proper ship in the future.

Directory structure:
source - all the project source
doc - documentation
doc/html - doxygen generated source doc
prototypes - previous versions of the code